The paper is about face recognition using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) category. The paper also discusses the impact of big data on recognition performance, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions real-world security certification scenarios, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM) and cryptography and security (cs.CR) categories.
